Package: LinkDeplete
Title: Within-Season Depletion Model for Crustacean Stock Assessment
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Simon", "de Lestang", , "simon.delestang@dpird.wa.gov.au",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fits a Leslie depletion model linked across seasons via a 
    random walk on recruitment using RTMB. Supports multiple CPUE series 
    (depletion and biomass indices), time-varying catchability, and 
    forward projection to target reference points. Includes diagnostic 
    plotting and privacy-mode output for presentations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
    RTMB,
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    magrittr,
    ggplot2,
    patchwork,
    scales,
    zoo
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
